short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hides the correct answer and rationale in the SAT速 Question Bank.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Effectively spend your time using the SAT速 Question Bank by hiding the answer to the question you are working on. Once you have completed the question, press the "Reveal Answers" button to show the answer and rationale for that question.

The Question Bank Answer Hider works on the Student Question Bank and the Educator Question Bank. It does not collect information about your passwords or any sensitive information.
